title: [Faeilythe's Fashions, Entryway]
description: Pale mistwood walls are polished to a fine sheen, bringing out the deeper grey of the burls and knots of the wood.  White-painted oak frames the front double windows and the door, each inset with diamond-paned clear glaes, letting in beams of brilliant sunlight.  A passageway to the north side of the shop leads out to a garden portico.

paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest, out
